Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,两周前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Two weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:05.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一个无形的穹顶坠落在小镇上方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}an invisible dome crashed down on Chester's Mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:07.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,使我们与外部世界隔绝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}cutting us off from the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:10.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶为何降落在此或者隐藏着什么奥秘\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why the dome is here or what mysteries lie ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:11.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们仍然不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:13.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,它每天考验着我们的极限\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Every day it tests our limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:16.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,激发了我们内心至善至恶的一面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}bringing out the best and the worst in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:20.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有人说我们将永远被困在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Some say we'll be stuck here forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:24.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我们永远不会放弃寻找出路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but we will never stop fighting to find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:26.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我正在接收电子邮件\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm getting e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,信号变得越来越强烈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Signal's getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:29.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,信号来源于这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's coming from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:30.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 我希望你知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}James, I expect you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:34.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去找莱尔乔姆利\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Talk to Lyle Chumley.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不，不，快，快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, no, no. Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:37.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她快被湖水淹死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was drowning in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:38.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她莫名其妙出现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She just appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:40.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道她从哪里冒出来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have no idea where she came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:44.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你25年前曾许诺\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You made a promise 25 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:47.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,会确保我们埋葬的不会重见天日\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to make sure that what we buried stayed buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:50.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看起来像是安琪在凶手身上留下了伤痕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Looks like Angie got a piece of whoever did this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是一只手的指尖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Those are the fingertips of a hand--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:53.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一只大手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a big hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:53.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一只男人的手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A man's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,88年夏天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}"Summer '88."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,莱尔 山姆和波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}"Lyle, Sam and Pauline."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:00:59.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:01.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这上面有什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:03.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是 我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's... me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:06.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有足够的食物支持我们的那一天就要到来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Day's coming when there won't be enough food to sustain us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:07.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们有必要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It may become necessary--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:08.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,减少人口数量了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to thin the herd.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:13.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是个人口普查 来帮你决定谁生谁死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}this is a census, to help you decide who lives and who dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:25.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,上午好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:27.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道它多有效\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not sure how good it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:29.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,它会有效的 只要你用我们的普查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is if you're using the census
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:31.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来解决人口问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to address our population problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:33.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 我需要了解我们目前的情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, got to see where we stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:35.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们了解我们的情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, we know where we stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要的是健康 有实用技能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We need people who are healthy, with practical skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:40.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可以多付出少索取的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}who give more than they take.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:41.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以 下一个是谁呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:43.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:46.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她是穹顶之下的第一个宝宝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was the first dome baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:51.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她母亲哈丽特 是主日学校的老师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her mother's Harriet-- she teaches Sunday school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哈丽特还能做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What else does Harriet do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:57.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:00.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她是一个 单身妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's a... single mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:01.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是个有信仰的女人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a woman of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:04.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆 我们的粮食供应正在缩减\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Jim, our food supplies are dwindling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:08.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能任由感情支配我们的行动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We can't let these emotions dictate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这没那么简单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It won't be easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我和这些人一起长大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen, I grew up with these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:13.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我被选中领导大家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was chosen to lead them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:16.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不会摇晃这棵大树 除非我已经明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not gonna shake the tree until I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁可以承受自己的分量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}who can carry their own weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:19.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而谁不可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and who can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你怎么才能确认呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But how will you be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:23.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:28.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许穹顶会指引我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe the dome will guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:30.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:37.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要去学校\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm headed to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们的风车发电项目真的有进展了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Our windmill power project is really coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听着 丽贝卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen, Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们会度过难关的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we're gonna get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要你带领我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}As long as you're leading us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:02.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:04.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,根据我们在安吉的指甲里发现的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Did Phil I.D. Angie's killer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,菲尔查到杀死她的凶手了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}from the stuff we found under her fingernails?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:14.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个死胡同 没有办法比对DNA\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's a dead end-- there's no way to run the DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:17.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,更何况在磁化事件后一半的镇民都可能有划痕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And half the town probably has scratches after the magnetization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:20.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡 佩恩认为切斯特镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rebecca Pine thinks Chester's Mill
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,无法自给自足多久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}can't sustain itself for much longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她和吉姆想利用人口普查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and she and Jim want to use the census
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来决定谁生谁死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to decide who lives and who doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 这听起来很疯狂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know. It sounds crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:34.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 老吉姆总是有上帝情结\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. Big Jim's always had a God complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:37.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道他们有一个计划 我们需要弄明白那是什么计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know they have a plan; we need to find out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:38.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我需要你的帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I could use the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,芭比站在哪边呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where does Barbie stand on all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在吉姆一边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}On Jim's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:47.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要谈谈你灭绝计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We need to talk about your extermination plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-那是减少人口的方法 -好吧 随便什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Reduction option. - Okay, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:00.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你看 我知道我们需要做最坏的打算 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look, I know that we need to prepare for the worst, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:03.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但如果那一天真的发生了 我需要清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But if that day happens, I want to be clear--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:06.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,除非大家都同意否则不能有任何行动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}no one acts unless we both agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:07.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听着 芭比\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen, Barbie, I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我和你一样不希望见到这一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}want that day to get here any more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有你的话 切斯特镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look, Chester's Mill couldn't have survived
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都不会安然度过过去的几天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the past few days without you--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,磁场问题 农作物 血雨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the magnets, the crops, the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们需要采取下一步动作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If we need to take that next step,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们会一起行动的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:21.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哈丽特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Harriet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这里没有那么多人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这让我觉得爱丽丝有一个大家庭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It makes me feel like Alice has a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的 没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们都是一家人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}One big family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 有你照顾大家真是太幸运了 对吧 芭比\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey, we're so lucky to have you take care of us. Right, Barbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:36.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果这个地方的食物供应不足\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If this place runs out of food,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,希望我们不会变成大家的公愤吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}let's hope that we're not on the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,年鉴可不会说谎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yearbooks don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是25年前的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's from 25 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 这是你的私事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey, this is kind of personal,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-但你在这上面放探针标记了吗 -乔 拜托\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- but do you have probe marks? - Joe, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的高等生物理论还是留着去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Save your theory on intelligent life-forms of the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,演讲吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for a TED talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这能解释她失忆 和她几十年来都没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Explain her memory loss, and the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,变老的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}she hasn't aged in decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可能是穹顶派她来的呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe the dome sent her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就像我妈一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It sent my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是 梅兰妮是个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, Melanie's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-穹顶派来的都是幻象 但我们是摸不着的 -好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- The dome sent an avatar; you can't grab an avatar. - Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:20.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不管她到底是什么 我们还是不要乱碰为好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}whatever she is, let's not manhandle her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,既然她不可能是梅兰妮 克鲁斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And since there's no way she's actually Melanie Cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那么我们就不该那样子称呼她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}then we probably shouldn't call her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:25.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那我们该叫她什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then what should we call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我应该知道我的名字是什么的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I should know what my name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我却不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以让他知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We should show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,呃 不行 他最不想听到的估计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh, yeah, no, the last thing he wants to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:39.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是你发现了一口1988年的不老泉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}is that you found the fountain of youth in 1988.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还穿着和昨天一样的衣服呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rockin' the same clothes as yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,太忙了 所以昨晚没回家吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Too busy to come home last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 茱莉亚在这里吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Is Julia here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不在 她留了字条说一会儿就回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. She left a note saying she'll be back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们几个那么早起床干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you guys doing up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-我们要跟茱莉亚聊聊 -我们收到了电子邮件\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- We need to talk to Julia... - Uh, we got e-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们什么时候收到了电子邮件\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You got e-mails when?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就昨天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们居然现在才告诉我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And you're just telling me about this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们都收到了邮件 然后突然就没信号了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We all got e-mails, until the signal was blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:09.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后这就突然出现了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And this popped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,该页面无法打开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}"This page can't be displayed."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得是军队屏蔽了我们的信号 还是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You think the military's blocking us, or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这不是正常的网页\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's not the standard response.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果信号能够回来 我们就可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We get that signal back, we can communicate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,跟外界联系了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}with the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 带我去你们连接上信号的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey, I want you to take me to where this came through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,恶魔将驱汝入狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The devil shall cast some of you into prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,纵汝垂死挣扎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that ye may be tried;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,汝将受十日磨难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}ye shall have tribulation ten days:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,心存不死之念\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}be thou faithful unto death,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,汝将重获生存之冠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I will give you a crown of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,站起来 莱尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}On your feet, Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:46.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是来放我出去的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You came to set me free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我妈说你知道原因 所以我就来找你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My mother said you had answers; I want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不仅可以告诉你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can do better than tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还可以带你去看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让我出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:04.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把这个拷上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Put these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么可以这样呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}O ye of little faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你绑架了丽贝卡 还企图杀了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You kidnapped Rebecca and you tried to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她妨碍到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was standing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的开心时光了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in the way of the Rapture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我放你出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If I'm gonna break you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,至少得把你的双手铐住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want your hands together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就当是在祈祷吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Think of it as a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-多谢你过来 -小猪怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Thanks for coming over. - How's the piglet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该是流感\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think it's a flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 太迟了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry. It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:42.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我比较担心其他的几只\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm worried about the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:45.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她是一头新生猪 其他的都很健壮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was a newborn. The others are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就算是流感 他们也能熬过去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If it's a flu, they'll fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道 人也有可能会被感染的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know,people can catch this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我没事 贝斯也没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm fine. So is Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:55.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们跟小猪接触的时候都很小心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We've been careful about contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:55.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你有手推车吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you have a wheelbarrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:02.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,最好能避免跟病猪接触\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No sense touching her more than you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,万事皆有因果\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everything happens for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,无线网的信号没了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This Wi-Fi signal's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们之前来的时候就没有了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It disappeared when we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以 你是说这里是信号最强的是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So, you said this is where it was strongest, right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的 这个柜子也很诡异\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yep. Because not enough's creepy about that locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要去找东西撬开它看看里面有什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm gonna have to go find something to pry this open with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,呃 里面空空如也\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh, there's nothing in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是怎么知道的 这个柜子被上锁了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But you don't know that-- it's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道密码的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How do you know that combination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:56.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得这个柜子以前是我用的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think this was my locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在1988年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in 1988.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等等 这是在开玩笑吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Okay, I-is this some kind of joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是老天开的玩笑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Played on us by the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,像她吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Looks like her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,讲不通啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:34.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,难道穹顶就说得通了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And the dome does?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 你都可以做照片里这个女孩的女儿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, you could be this girl's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,芭比\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Barbie...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:42.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道那种一直被当做外人的感觉吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you know what it's like to be a stranger here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不想再这样下去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't want to be one anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不确定我能不能帮到你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not sure I can help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,信号已经没了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The signal's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就来帮我们查清楚她到底是谁吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Help us figure out who she really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:01.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡喜欢把工作带回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rebecca likes to take her work home with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:19.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或者是不想在学校被人看到她的工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or doesn't want to be seen doing it at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她去过淤泥很多的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's been somewhere with a lot of muck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,早饭吃鸡蛋 晚饭吃血样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Eggs for breakfast, blood samples for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:34.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不管她在干什么 她都做了防范措施\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Whatever she's doing, she's taking precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:35.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的 她还有一本记录了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. She's got a calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,食物保质期和资源殆尽日期的备忘录\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of when we run out of food and resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:39.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她真的觉得世界末日到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She really does think it's the end of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们的科学老师居然加入了教会 真是稀奇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Our science teacher in prayer group. That's new.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:56.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 她确实对上帝创造的物种\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, she does have an interest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很感兴趣啊 猪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in one of God's creatures, pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,血样 兽医书\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Blood work, vet books,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,门口擦鞋垫上的淤泥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}mud on the doormat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在这附近有养猪的农场寥寥无几\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There are a few farms around here with pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们去看看她最近是不是去过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's see if she paid a visit to any of them recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:24.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:28.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在研究风车发电吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You working on the windmills?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:49.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们真的要在茱莉亚的新闻办公室用缩微胶卷吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're supposed to use microfilm in Julia's newspaper office?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:51.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没搞错吧 这是石器时代研究事物的方法啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Seriously? This is how they found things in the Stone Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对啊 我们不能直接搜索梅兰妮的名字吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, we can't search by Melanie's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:56.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不能 只能一个个看下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. You just got to scroll and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我怀念网络 怀念我的手机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I miss the Internet, I miss my cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怀念发短信 怀念寿司\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I miss texting, I miss sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:04.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,记录数据库什么都没查到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, the Hall of Records turned up nothing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是最后一个我能想到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is the last place that I can think to look...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:09.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能找东西的地方了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for whatever it is that we might find.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮没有出现在1987年或是1989年的年鉴里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Melanie wasn't in the '87 or '89 yearbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许独立报社在1988年报道过他们家搬到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe The Independent ran an article about why her family
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,切斯特磨坊镇来的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}came to Chester's Mill in 1988.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或是为什么她离开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or why she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:22.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在这连西红柿突破重量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In a town where Betsy Van Needles' record-breaking tomato
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都能上头条的镇子上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}makes the front page,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我得说 我们干得不错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'd say we have a pretty good shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:26.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,伙计们 快看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Guys, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:34.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮 克鲁斯 神秘失踪 未被寻回\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Melanie Cross went missing and was never found.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:35.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那家人不久前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The family moved "To
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:38.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,刚从齐尼思搬到切斯特镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Chester's Mill from Zenith a short time ago."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:39.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,齐尼思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Zenith?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也是从那个镇出来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's the same town that I'm from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我就说 我看你面熟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought you looked familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:55.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮一家住在古橡城24号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Melanie's family lived at 24 Old Oak Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果她在柜子前面的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If she remembered the combo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能想起来柜子密码组合的话 那么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}when she stood in front of her locker, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是说 如果我们带她回家的话 她会想起更多事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You think she'll remember more if we take her to the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:01.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:06.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 她想不起来的 因为她不是 她不是梅兰妮 克鲁斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, she won't. Because she's not... she's not Melanie Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:07.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是不可能的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's just no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想去那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我必须得去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那我们闯入那栋房子的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do we say when we barge in on the family
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:19.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么跟现在住在那里的家庭解释呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that lives there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让我来处理\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You let me handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:30.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我 我妈现在还活着吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Talk to me. Tell me how my mother's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:33.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们不是计划好了吗 切断制动管路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We had a plan: severed brake lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:35.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,盗出尸体 傻瓜牧师考金斯 他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}pilfered corpses, that idiot Reverend Coggins, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,愿上帝安息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}God rest his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我妈妈造成自杀的假象 你帮了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My mother faked her suicide, and you helped her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很爱她 詹姆斯 依然如故\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I loved her very much, James, I still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:43.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她抛弃了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She abandoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那是为了保护你 她知道穹顶要降临了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To protect you. She knew the dome was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那些画里的粉色星星\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The pink stars in the paintings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她要在被带走前逃出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She had to get out before she was taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:51.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:54.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你爸对她有别的计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your father had other plans for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他不知道她还活着吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He has no idea that she's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:00.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:02.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那山姆呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What about Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,波林只相信让我帮她逃出\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Pauline only trusted me to help her escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:10.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么样的母亲会自己离开让自己的儿子留在这个地狱里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What kind of a mother leaves her son behind in this hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得她认为 穹顶会跟着她而放过你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think she thought the dome would follow her and spare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还要去参加她的葬礼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I had to go to her funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:20.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她把我留在这儿 是她让我变成大吉姆·兰尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She left me here. She left me to turn into Big Jim Rennie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听着 你妈妈信任我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look, your mother trusts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:30.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这九年来波林都是这么和我联系的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For nine years that's how Pauline stayed in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,用明信片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With postcards?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:42.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:45.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这都是从不同地方寄来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They're from all different places,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:46.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但上面什么都没有写\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but there's nothing on 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:48.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:50.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她做了这些东西 你把它们翻过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She made those. Turn 'em over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:53.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她的画\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看着熟悉吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do those look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:04.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这都是自从穹顶降临以来发生的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is all the stuff that happened since the dome came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那个蛋 那些蝴蝶 还有红雨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The egg, the butterflies, the red rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果她在穹顶之外 她怎么可能知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If she's out there, how could she possibly know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶这下面发生了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}what's going on under here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,波林看到的远不止粉色星星\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Pauline saw a lot more than pink stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我没看见什么风车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't see any windmills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:36.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你偷了我的卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You stole my card,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还向我说谎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想做什么呢 丽贝卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you doing, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在想办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm finding a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当穹顶刚刚降临的时候 我开始拜访农场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}When the dome first came down, I started visiting farms,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,观察庄稼和牲畜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}monitoring crops and livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,汤姆 蒂尔登 有一头病猪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tom Tilden had a sick pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:51.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是流感\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:56.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,鸡蛋里有什么 丽贝卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's inside the eggs, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你说你会全力拯救小镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You said you'd do what it takes to save this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,鸡蛋里的东西就是你的法宝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's inside those eggs is how you're gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们前门没锁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They left the front door unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:25.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可能在穹顶降临那天去了西湖参加游行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Probably went to the parade in Westlake
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,被挡在穹顶之外了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and got trapped outside the dome on Dome Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真走运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Lucky them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们都还没有吃完早饭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They didn't even finish breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有个孩子不用做完代数作业了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Some kid didn't have to finish his algebra homework
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还逃出了这个仓鼠球\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and avoided the hamster ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真是一箭双雕啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Double win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那个看起来眼熟吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Does it look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我记不得任何东西了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:48.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为没什么可以想起来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because there's nothing to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只感到悲伤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All I feel is sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,回到家里但是家人不在身边的感觉糟透了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It sucked having to walk through my house with my family gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在安琪过世后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And after Angie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很庆幸房子塌了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm glad the place fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我该怎么和一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How am I supposed to compete with a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他觉得来自很遥远的外星系的女孩儿竞争呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}he thinks is from a galaxy far, far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我肯定他想要帮点忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sure he's just trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,别指望能消除我的嫉妒和被抛弃的感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't undermine my feelings of jealousy and abandonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:21.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是既然我们都聊到这儿了 你和朱莉娅出什么事儿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But since we're chatting, what's up with you and Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,拜托 你摆出一副 快原谅我 的样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on. You show up with the "Please forgive me" Face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:27.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她在你到这儿之前就离开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She left before you got there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她一定不想听你说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}so she didn't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你肯定做了什么超级坏的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Whatever you did was super bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你眉毛刚刚抽搐了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your eyebrow just twitched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我真高兴能和你这样小小地聊一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm really glad we could have this little chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,芭比 诺尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Barbie, Nore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:43.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 天哪 这是我做的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, my God. I made these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我曾经看到窗外 发现它们在掉落\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I used to look out the window and see them falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她看见星星掉落了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She saw stars fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:49.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是粉红色的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They were pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 就在那儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:52.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还出去找过它们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I went out to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那是我们发现小穹顶的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's where we found the mini-dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:55.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们要去那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We got to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:57.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔 别慌\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Joe, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶不知怎么就出现了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The dome came out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就此改变了我们的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and changed our lives forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:03.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安吉被杀了 我可能永远都不会知道答案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Angie was killed-- I might never know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是个机会 让我找寻真相\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is a chance to find an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去找到那该死的答案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to find one damn answer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,即便不是为了我而找\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}even if it's not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该去树林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think we should look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 那我们就动身\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right. We go to the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:23.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果一无所获就回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If we find nothing, we go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:25.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,跑了六家农场 一无所获\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Six farms and nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有一家呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Still one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 可是按照农民们说的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, but according to the farmers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:35.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,瑞贝卡只是在观察牲口和作物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rebecca was only monitoring livestock and crop yields.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:39.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她说人口普查是为了确定粮食存量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She said the point of the town census was to inventory resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:42.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:43.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许她没有谋划什么坏事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe she's not planning anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 你没听到她的语气\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, no, no. You didn't hear what I heard in her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或是看到她拿酸雨泼莱尔的场景\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or see her douse Lyle with that acid rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,尽管这也许不是第一次我看走眼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Though it wouldn't be the first time I've misjudged someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,其实我并不太了解你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't really know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在树林里待太久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hell, I've been out in the woods for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有时候我甚至都不认得自己了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}there are days I don't even know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我知道我以前遭到过背叛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But I do know that I've been betrayed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:12.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想说什么 萨姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you getting at, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,林子大了 什么鸟都有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}People are full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,确实是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:26.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你计划了多久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How long you been planning this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那些猪我观察了好几周了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'd been monitoring the pig for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在家检测血液 观察病毒怎样侵袭细胞\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Testing blood at my house to see how the virus affected cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你打算什么时候再告诉我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}When were you gonna tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当一切就绪的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Once everything was ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是我为什么要到这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's why I needed to get in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:41.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要混合猪流感和人的流感病毒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to mix the swine flu with samples of influenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,几小时后 混合病毒就足够有效\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In a few hours, the recombinant virus inside those eggs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能让镇上四分之一的人丧生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}will be strong enough to infect one quarter of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想下毒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You want to release it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想你去做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想让我来扮演上帝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You want me to play God?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你说过你想看谁能承受生命之重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You said you wanted to see who could carry their own weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是方法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is how.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这不是神学 这是进化学\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's not God-- it's-it's Darwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,符合适者生存\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's survival of the fittest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-也就是说 我们自己也可能会中招 -对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Meaning we're at risk, too. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:17.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,病毒是上天自然选择的最好方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A virus is nature's way of leveling the playing field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这想法太疯狂了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:24.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是上天的仁慈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,7天以后 我们就弹尽粮绝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In seven days, we run out of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,14天后 人们会饥饿无比\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In 14, people will be starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,21天后 我们会自相残杀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In 21, we'll turn on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:36.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在就是做出行动的最佳时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The time to act is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:41.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,病毒是怎么进入穹顶的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How'd this virus get inside the dome?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:44.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,它一直都在 只是一直在休眠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's always been here, dormant in nature for...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:47.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,沉睡了数周 数月 也许数年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}weeks, months... maybe years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是说 穹顶就像孵化器\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You mean like an incubator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是它让着一切发生的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The dome made this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-你说我妈是个预言家 -不 我是说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- You're saying my mom's a prophet? - No, I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这些事件将我们推向世界末日\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that these events brought us closer to the apocalypse,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:09.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当生活焚烧地球\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}when the world's gonna burn with the sacred fires
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:11.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,字幕我们的骨灰就将飘向天堂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and our ashes are gonna float up into the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那时 我会与波林团聚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's when I'm gonna be with Pauline again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:15.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这场雨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我以为是世界末日的预兆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought presaged the end of days,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:20.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只是因为那是我收到的最后一张卡片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but that's just 'cause that's the last card I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不关它是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, whatever it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,瑞贝卡阻止了它真是万幸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}it was a good thing that Rebecca stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:26.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 如果她打乱了穹顶的计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey! If she interfered with the dome's plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们都会诅咒进入炼狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we're gonna be condemned to purgatory
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:29.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,永远生活在这破玩意儿里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}under this thing for all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-永世不得超生 -莱尔 莱尔 冷静点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Forever, forever, forever. - Lyle, Lyle, Lyle, settle down,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不然我会再把你拷上 听着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or the cuffs are going back on. Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这些都是穹顶出现之前得到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}these couldn't have come after the dome came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们不知道它将怎样结束\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe we don't know how it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:41.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,邮政关门了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Postcards stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但她确实每天都写日志\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But she did write in the journal every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我猜你是这一切的关键也写在日志中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I bet you the key to this is in the journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,呃 我叔叔来过 在葬礼之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh, my uncle came and picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他拿走了她的一堆东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a bunch of her stuff after the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:54.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她不会想让萨姆拿走她的日志 不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She wouldn't want Sam to have her journal. Not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:56.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-你们到底有什么秘密 -这不重要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- What is it with you guys, anyway? - It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们去把日志抢回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's just go get the journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:22:00.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-不 不 -你不想了解你妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Oh, no, no. - You don't want to know about your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有那个被杀的女孩儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What about that girl that got killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:04.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安吉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Angie?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:10.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很清楚的记得 我坐在门廊看着蔷薇酒吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have a real clear view of the Sweetbriar Rose from my porch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:12.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我看到你等她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've watched you waiting for her
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:14.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,接她下班\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to pick her up after her shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:16.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-很抱歉她去世了 -等等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I'm really sorry about what happened to her... - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:19.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得我妈把安吉的死也写下来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You think my mom put Angie's murder in her journal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:26.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 谢天谢地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:29.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡让你们来帮忙的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Did Rebecca send you to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-帮什么忙 -她说有一头猪出问题了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Help with what? - She said it'd be just the one pig,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:33.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但她说得不对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but she was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:34.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是好多头都有问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There are more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:36.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就今天早上开始的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:38.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,十几头猪都病了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A dozen of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:42.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把健康的那些隔离\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Quarantine the healthy animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:44.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,原来丽贝卡在厨房里搞得是这个名堂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is what Rebecca was messing around with in her kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,猪瘟就是他们的消除计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That pig virus is their extermination plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:48.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 而且她根本不清楚猪瘟有多严重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, and she doesn't know how strong it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:51.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们得在他们释放病毒前找到他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We've got to find them before they release it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:52.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们会在哪里释放呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where would they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,公共场合 交通繁忙的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Someplace busy, someplace public.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,大吉姆会在蔷薇酒吧召开小镇集会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Big Jim's having a town meeting at the Sweetbriar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:22:58.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们应该就是要去那儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's where they'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:06.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚就是带我来了这里 看的迷你穹顶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is where Julia brought me, to show me the mini-dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:11.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮 你去哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Melanie, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:14.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她要去迷你穹顶那儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's going to the exact spot where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:33.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还好么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:36.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:38.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想起来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:40.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那天晚上 我和波林 佛多一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was night. I came here looking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:43.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来这里找粉色星星的坠落之处\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for where the pink stars fell with Pauline Verdreaux.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:45.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-和朱尼尔的妈妈 -是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Junior's mom? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:47.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,萨姆 佛多也在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We were with Sam Verdreaux
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.08,0:23:48.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有莱尔 乔密\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and Lyle Chumley.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:49.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们是我们的男朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They were our boyfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:51.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你和萨姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You and Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:52.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的头要炸开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My head is exploding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:53.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:55.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,之后怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:56.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:59.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个地点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:01.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让你找回了你的记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's bringing back your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:03.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你想对自己的身份了解的更多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If you want to know more about who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.06,0:24:04.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就得再站上去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}then you have to get back on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:14.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.41,0:24:16.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看起来像是陨石 正在发光发热呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Looks like a meteor. It's glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.29,0:24:17.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们去看看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's go see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.05,0:24:21.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们找到了陨石\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We found a meteorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:23.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.81,0:24:29.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该碰碰它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe we're supposed to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.13,0:24:39.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当我们碰到它时 它啪的一声打开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}When we touched it, it... it cracked open.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:43.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,大家都没事吧 你没事吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is everybody okay? You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.21,0:24:44.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,里面有个蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There was an egg inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.78,0:24:46.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 我的天 那是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, my God... What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.16,0:24:48.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮 不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Melanie, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.61,0:24:50.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-梅兰妮 -你在干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Melanie. - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.56,0:24:52.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,放回去 不要动它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Put it back. Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.54,0:24:53.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我拿起了它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.37,0:24:56.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想保护它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I wanted to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.17,0:24:57.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮 把它放回去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Melanie, put it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.19,0:24:57.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮 你要去哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Melanie! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.91,0:24:59.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-梅兰妮 回来 -梅 梅兰妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Melanie, come back! - Mel-Melanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.98,0:25:00.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Melanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.62,0:25:03.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,萨姆要我把它放回去 但是我没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sam told me to put it back, but I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.96,0:25:05.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,丢掉它 梅兰妮 把它放回去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Drop it, Melanie. Put it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.58,0:25:06.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.52,0:25:09.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,发生了什么 那声音快要了我的命了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What is happening?! The sound is killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.76,0:25:32.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我是梅兰妮 克鲁斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am Melanie Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.18,0:25:36.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想这里就是我死去的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I think this is where I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.59,0:26:05.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,病毒准备好了么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is the virus ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.73,0:26:06.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.38,0:26:09.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你准备好了么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.48,0:26:12.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没人告诉过我 做决断者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No one tells you what it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.93,0:26:16.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是什么样的感受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}...being the one who has to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.21,0:26:18.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你被选中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You were chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.42,0:26:20.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是因为你足够强大 足以做决定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because you're strong enough to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.81,0:26:23.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道的 我曾经历过这样的考验\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, I was tested like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.33,0:26:25.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.69,0:26:27.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是我的妻子 波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was my wife, Pauline.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.94,0:26:30.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她病了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.82,0:26:32.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She started...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.03,0:26:36.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能看见一些东西 变得偏执妄想 像中了邪一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}seeing things, got paranoid, had these spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.47,0:26:37.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她得了精神病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was mentally ill;
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.40,0:26:39.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那 那不是你的错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that's... that's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.68,0:26:41.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道她需要帮助 所以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I knew she needed help, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.16,0:26:46.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我找到了一个地方 离这里隔了几个镇子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I found this facility... A few towns away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.26,0:26:51.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她求我 不要把她带去那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She begged me not to take her there,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.26,0:26:53.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,并保证她会好起来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}promised she'd get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.88,0:26:58.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以我让步了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I gave in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.29,0:27:01.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没带她去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Didn't make her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.88,0:27:06.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为我爱她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}'Cause I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.99,0:27:09.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我相信有爱就足够了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I believed that would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.02,0:27:12.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但事实并非如此\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.73,0:27:16.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她自杀了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She took her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.36,0:27:19.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.12,0:27:23.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我做了那艰难的决定 选择正确的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If I'd made the tough choice, the right choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.06,0:27:26.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许她真会好起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}...maybe she would have gotten better.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.40,0:27:29.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许她现在还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe she'd be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.37,0:27:36.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这一次我要做对的选择\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This time I'll make that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.80,0:27:52.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我八岁时 我妈妈去世了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My mother died when I was eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.66,0:27:55.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她的心脏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her heart just...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.16,0:27:57.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就 就那样停止了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you know... stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.33,0:28:02.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们当时正骑着单车绕过海军基地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We were riding our bikes around the army base,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.10,0:28:03.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,突然她就\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and suddenly she was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.35,0:28:06.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去世了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.99,0:28:09.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我问我爸爸 为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I asked my dad why,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.11,0:28:12.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他说 有时候就是没有为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and he said, "Sometimes there are no answers."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.67,0:28:17.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以我爱上了科学\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And that's why I turned to science.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.37,0:28:23.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你观察够仔细 那就一定会有答案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If you look hard enough, there is an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.04,0:28:33.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你得把它投到水中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You'll need to distribute it in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.85,0:28:38.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,人群多的地方会增加感染的几率\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A crowd will increase the rate of infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.73,0:28:40.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道这是哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.90,0:28:44.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在1988年的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Back in 1988,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.19,0:28:45.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你 山姆 波林 还有莱尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you, Sam, Pauline and Lyle
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.96,0:28:47.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是最初的四双手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}were the original four hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.57,0:28:48.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们也找到一颗蛋是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And you found an egg, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.10,0:28:51.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后某个混账也因此杀了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And some jackass killed her because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.60,0:28:53.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你确定你没看见是谁推你吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you sure you didn't see who pushed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.29,0:28:55.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,肯定不是波林 她当时已经\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It wasn't Pauline-- she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.58,0:28:57.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,吓惨了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.18,0:28:59.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,莱尔当时很愤怒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Lyle was really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.90,0:29:01.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以是山姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So was Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.18,0:29:04.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想保护那颗蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I just wanted to protect the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.34,0:29:07.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.67,0:29:09.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,感觉是一块石头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Feels like a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.39,0:29:14.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对啊  外太空飞来的一块石头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, a rock from outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.84,0:29:33.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,首字母是MC\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Initial's "M.C."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.07,0:29:41.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Melanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.09,0:29:46.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想这应该是你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}...I believe this is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.87,0:29:55.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我已经死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If I died...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.50,0:29:58.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那我是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}then what am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.78,0:29:59.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么又会在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.77,0:30:02.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的尸骨又在哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And where are your bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.56,0:30:09.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想山姆 佛多肯定知道答案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I bet Sam Verdreaux could answer those questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.75,0:30:11.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.20,0:30:13.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那天晚上他在场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He was there that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.25,0:30:15.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果这一切都是真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And if all this is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.24,0:30:17.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那他这几天都已经见到过梅兰妮了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}he's seen Melanie in the last couple days.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.17,0:30:18.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 是他帮茱莉亚救了她的命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, he helped Julia save her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.34,0:30:20.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你难道会忘记你的前女友吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wouldn't you remember your ex-girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.76,0:30:22.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是他装得好像完全不认识她似的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But he acts like he never even knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.97,0:30:24.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许他不是在演戏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe it's not an act, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.62,0:30:26.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许就是他杀了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And maybe he's the one who killed her.
