Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.09,0:36:58.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔 过来下 帮我  帮我扶他起来 加把劲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Joe, come on. Help me. Help me get him up. Come on.
