Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.78,0:37:08.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,接下来是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.81,0:37:13.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,消除计划过后又是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What comes after an extermination plot?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.40,0:37:15.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿  我们撑过了今天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey, we made it through the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.49,0:37:18.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那些制定计划的人进了监狱了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And the guys behind that plan are behind bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.37,0:37:21.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊  大吉姆现在可能正躺在凹凸不平的小床上呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Big Jim's probably lying on a lumpy cot,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.59,0:37:23.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,想念着他自己舒适的床呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}missing his own bed right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.34,0:37:26.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊  他今晚可不好过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. He's had better nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.06,0:37:28.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们现在可以好好利用一下人口调查了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now we can put the census to good use--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.45,0:37:31.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,想出该如何分配资源\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}figure out how to share resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.35,0:37:38.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.37,0:37:40.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.82,0:37:44.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我大清早出现在你的门前讲着一大堆疯狂的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I showed up on your door at dawn with an insane theory--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.13,0:37:46.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你却听得连眼都没眨一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you didn't blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.90,0:37:49.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你很能让人信服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're pretty convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.53,0:37:50.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你相信我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.76,0:37:52.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这对我来说很有意义\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That means something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.21,0:37:59.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.02,0:38:06.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.16,0:38:09.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 茱莉亚  嘿 听着 你得听我给你说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, Julia. Hey, listen. You got to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.29,0:38:11.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,今晚不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.79,0:38:26.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.43,0:38:32.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.82,0:38:34.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 那就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.83,0:38:46.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对不起  我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry. I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.17,0:38:47.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道我在想些什么 我会走的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know what I was thinking. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.47,0:38:48.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-我  -不 不 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I... - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.36,0:38:51.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,请留下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.60,0:38:53.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让我们别那么尴尬\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's not make it weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.13,0:38:56.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-好的 -好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Okay. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.16,0:39:03.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,明天整个小镇都需要答案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The whole town's gonna want answers in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.72,0:39:06.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我需要你的智慧 来告诉我答案是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I could really use your help coming up with what those are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.56,0:39:18.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-蜂蜜  -好的 谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Honey? - Yeah, thanks.
